    <p class="pg-sub">Two of the most popular adaptogens in 2026, but they serve fundamentally different purposes. Ashwagandha reduces cortisol and manages stress. Lion's mane stimulates Nerve Growth Factor and enhances cognition. This evidence-based comparison will help you choose the right one — or determine if you should take both.</p>
